last_episode_to_air.overview: Khoob Seerat is a 2020 Pakistani television series premiered on Geo Entertainment on 17 February 2020. It is produced by Abdullah Kadwani and Asad Qureshi under their banner 7th Sky Entertainment. It features Kiran Haq, Nimra Khan and Agha Ali in lead roles.
